msgctxt "Description|"
msgid "Time Series Descriptives"
msgstr "Deskriptif Seri Waktu"

msgctxt "DescriptivesTimeSeriesForm|"
msgid ""
"Time Series Descriptives allows the user to obtain descriptive statistics "
"and descriptive plots for univariate time-series."
msgstr ""
"Deskriptif Seri Waktu mengizinkan pengguna untuk memperoleh statistik "
"deskriptif dan diagram deskriptif untuk seri waktu univariat."

msgctxt "DescriptivesTimeSeriesForm|"
msgid "Variable"
msgstr "Variabel"

msgctxt "DescriptivesTimeSeriesForm|"
msgid "A variable that is measured repeatedly over time."
msgstr "Variabel yang diukur secara berulang dari waktu."

msgctxt "DescriptivesTimeSeriesForm|"
msgid "Time"
msgstr "Waktu"

msgctxt "DescriptivesTimeSeriesForm|"
msgid ""
"Optional. Can either be an ordinal variable indicating the order of the "
"observations, or a text variable indicating the date/time stamp of the "
"observations. Combined date and time values should be in the standard format "
"'YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM:SS', where seconds (':SS') can also be omitted. Date-only "
"values should be in the format 'YYYY-MM-DD'. If a time variable is not "
"supplied, the row order of the data is used."
msgstr ""
"Opsional. Dapat baik variabel ordinal mengindikasikan urutan observasi, atau "
"variabel teks mengindikasikan tanggal/stempel waktu observasi. Nilai tanggal "
"dan waktu terkombinasi seharusnya dalam format standar 'YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM:"
"SS', di mana detik (':SS') juga dapat dihilangkan. Nilai hanya tanggal "
"seharusnya dalam format 'YYYY-MM-DD'. Jika variabel waktu tidak disertakan, "
"urutan baris data digunakan."

msgctxt "DescriptivesTimeSeriesForm|"
msgid "Transpose descriptives table"
msgstr "Transposkan tabel deskriptif"

msgctxt "DescriptivesTimeSeriesForm|"
msgid "Filter by"
msgstr "Filter berdasarkan"

msgctxt "DescriptivesTimeSeriesForm|"
msgid ""
"Filters the time series so only a specific range will be used for further "
"analyses. Row number refers to the row number in the spreadsheet. If a "
"'Time' variable is supplied it is also possible to filter by time index or "
"date, depending on the format of the 'Time' variable."
msgstr ""
"Menyaring seri waktu sehingga hanya rentang tertentu akan digunakan untuk "
"analisis lebih lanjut. Nomor baris mengacu nomor baris di lembar kerja. Jika "
"variabel 'Waktu' disertakan itu juga dapat menyaring berdasarkan indeks "
"waktu atau tanggal, tergantung pada format variabel 'Waktu'."

