msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Adjust how faceted panels share scales, axes and space. <b>Scale and axis "
"settings</b> decide whether panels use the same range, which axis lines are "
"drawn and where labels appear. <b>Layout settings</b> control panel sizes, "
"the position of the highest-value table, optional marginal plots and custom "
"axis titles"
msgstr ""
"Sesuaikan bagaimana panel berfaset membagikan skala, sumbu dan spasi. <b>"
"Pengaturan skala dan sumbu</b> memutuskan apakah panel menggunakan rentang "
"sama, yang mana garis sumbu digambar dan di mana label muncul. <b>Pengaturan "
"tata letak</b> mengontrol ukuran panel, posisi tabel nilai-tertinggi, "
"diagram margin opsional dan judul sumbu kustom"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Choose whether facet panels share a common scale (<i>fixed</i>) or get "
"individual ranges"
msgstr ""
"Pilih apakah panel faset membagikan skala umum (<i>tetap</i>) atau "
"mendapatkan rentang individu"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Decide which facet panels display axis lines"
msgstr "Putuskan yang mana panel faset menampilkan garis sumbu"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Control which tick-label texts are shown"
msgstr "Kontrol yang mana teks tabel-centang ditampilkan"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Controls where the summary table of highest values is placed inside each "
"facet"
msgstr ""
"Mengontrol di mana tabel ringkasan nilai tertinggi ditempatkan di dalam "
"setiap faset"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Allow facet panels to stretch freely along X, Y or both axes"
msgstr ""
"Izinkan panel faset untuk meregang secara bebas dengan sumbu X, Y atau kedua"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Adds aggregated rows/columns at the edges of the facet grid"
msgstr "Menambahkan baris/kolom teragregasi di tepi kisi faset"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Arrange panels when a grid variable is mapped. <b>Layout settings</b> set "
"the facet grid’s rows, columns and where the highest-values table appears, "
"<b>Scales and strip settings</b> decide whether panels share axes and where "
"the facet label strip is placed"
msgstr ""
"Susun panel ketika variabel kisi dipetakan. <b>Pengaturan tata telak</b> "
"mengatur baris, kolom kisi faset, dan di mana tabel nilai-tertinggi muncul, "
"<b>Pengaturan skala dan strip</b> memutuskan apakah panel membagikan sumbu "
"dan di mana strip label faset ditempatkan"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Fixed number of facet columns; 0 lets the layout pick automatically"
msgstr ""
"Jumlah tetap kolom faset; 0 membiarkan tata letak memilih secara otomatis"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Fixed number of facet rows; 0 lets the layout pick automatically"
msgstr ""
"Jumlah tetap baris faset; 0 membiarkan tata letak memilih secara otomatis"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Choose the corner where the summary table of highest values is drawn"
msgstr "Pilih sudut di mana tabel ringkasan nilai tertinggi digambargan"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Fixed panels share axes; free panels get independent X and/or Y scales"
msgstr ""
"Panel tetap membagikan sumbu; panel bebas mendapatkan skala X dan/atau Y "
"independen"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Location of the facet label strip"
msgstr "Lokasi strip label faset"

