msgstr "Geser garis akumulasi"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid "Add count variable"
msgstr "Tambahkan variabel hitungan"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid ""
"Allows you to specify an additional variable that contains the counts for "
"each category instead of letting the analysis compute frequencies "
"automatically. This is useful when the data are already aggregated (e.g., "
"each row represents a category with an associated frequency). If left empty, "
"counts are calculated directly from the selected variable."
msgstr ""
"Mengizinkan Anda untuk menetukan variabel tambahan yang berisi hitungan "
"untuk setiap kategori alih-alih membiarkan analisis menghitung frekuensi "
"secara otomatis. Ini berguna ketika data sudah diagregasikan (mis., setiap "
"baris merepresentasikan kategori dengan frekuensi yang diasosiasikan). Jika "
"kosong, hitungan dihitung secara langsung dari variabel terpilih."

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid "Mean (arithmetic)"
msgstr "Rerata (aritmatika)"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid ""
"Arithmetic mean of the data points; otherwise also colloquially called 'the "
"mean' or 'the average'. Calculated as the sum of all data points divided by "
"the number of data points."
msgstr ""
"Rerata aritmatika dari titik data; atau juga dalam sehari-hari disebut "
"dengan 'nilai rerata' atau 'rata-rata'. Dihitung sebagai jumlah semua titik "
"data dibagi dengan jumlah titik data."

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid "Mean (geometric)"
msgstr "Rerata (geometris)"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid ""
"Geometric mean of the data points; defined only for strictly positive "
"variables. Calculated as the product of all data points, raised to the power "
"of 1 divided by the number of points (the n-th root of the product)."
msgstr ""
"Rerata geometris dari titik data; ditentukan hanya untuk variabel yang "
"selalu positif. Dihitung sebagai produk semua titik data, dipangkatkan ke "
"pangkat 1 dibagi dengan jumah titik (akar ke-n dari produk)."

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid "Mean (harmonic)"
msgstr "Rerata (harmonis)"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid ""
"Harmonic mean of the data points; defined only for strictly positive "
"variables. Calculated as the number of data points divided by the sum of the "
"reciprocals of the data points."
msgstr ""
"Rerata harmonis dari titik data; ditentukan hanya untuk variabel yang selalu "
"positif. Dihitung sebagai jumlah titik data dibagi dengan jumlah kebalikan "
"dari titik data."

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid "Standard error of the arithmetic mean."
msgstr "Galat standar untuk rerata aritmatika."

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid "Confidence interval for the arithmetic mean"
msgstr "Interval kepercayaan untuk rerata aritmatika"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid "Type"
msgstr "Jenis"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid "1"
msgstr "1"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid "2 (SAS)"
msgstr "2 (SAS)"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
