msgstr "5"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid "6 (Minitab, SPSS)"
msgstr "6 (Tab mini, SPSS)"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid "7 (R)"
msgstr "7 (R)"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid "8"
msgstr "8"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid "9"
msgstr "9"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid ""
"Shifts the cumulative line so that it starts at the top-right corner of the "
"first bar instead of in the middle. This corresponds to the traditional "
"Pareto chart layout."
msgstr ""
"Menggeser garis kumulatif jadi itu dimulai dari sudut kanan atas batang "
"pertama alih-alih dari tengah. Ini sesuai dengan tata letak bagan Pareto "
"tradisional."

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid "Tilt x-axis labels"
msgstr "Miringkan label sumbu-x"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid ""
"Tilts the x-axis labels by 45 degrees to improve readability when there are "
"many long levels."
msgstr ""
"Memiringkan label sumbu-x sebesar 45 derajat untuk meningkatkan keterbacaan "
"ketika ada banyak tingkat panjang."

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid "Confidence interval"
msgstr "Interval kepercayaan"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid ""
"Method used to compute quantiles (see Hyndman & Fan, 1996; Langford, 2006, "
"for more information). The selection carries over to the inter-quartile "
"range (IQR) and box-plot calculations.  For ordinal variables, only types 1 "
"and 3 are supported; other types fall back to type 3.\n"
msgstr ""
"Metode yang digunakan untuk meghitung kuantil (lihat Hyndman & Fan; 1996; "
"Langford, 2006, untuk informasi lebih lanjut). Pemilihan dibawa pada rentang "
"antar-kuartil (IQR) dan penghitungan diagram kotak.  Untuk variabel ordinal, "
"hanya jenis 1 dan 3 didukung; jenis lain kembali ke 3.\n"
